				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "PAD played by the party when they step on the Great Door pincode pressure plate for the first time and are surprised by how it works. Players enter a 4-digit code using the pressure plates, the four lights above the door light up. If they fade again, the player knows they've entered the wrong code.\r\n\r\nMinsc can't be part of that."
